Package liber_application.model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Book
    The book class - representing a single physical book
    BookLoan
    BookLoan - class to store information of a book loan.
    Genre
    The genre entity It has no artificial key and a genre can currently not be altered once saved.
    Location
    A entity for location The lack of a artificial key makes it currently impossible to alter any saved Location name If you want to update a location you must make a new location and set the connected books to that
    User
    The user class.
